00:13:23.460 --> 00:13:24.060
Tu sais,

00:13:24.460 --> 00:13:24.940
Le.

00:13:27.700 --> 00:13:28.460
je

00:13:29.260 --> 00:13:30.420
Je l'ai revu plus tard.

